===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /l蓻虇'n瑟蕛蓹n/

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''lenition'''
# ''(Celtic linguistics)'' a weakening of [[articulation]], a consonant鈥檚 becoming [[lenis]] or [[soft]]

